    "    # README\n",
    "    readme = f\"\"\"\n",
    "Replica-SWAP boundary stochastic irreversibility pilot\n",
    "\n",
    "This is a self-contained computational analogue study.\n",
    "It does not implement AdS/CFT geometry or a gravitational bulk.\n",
    "It tests whether a replica-SWAP control perturbation, which is entanglement-sensitive through the SWAP/Renyi structure, is operationally associated with boundary-level path-probability asymmetry.\n",
    "\n",
